room_title: Escape room "Escape Atlantis" by Game the Room in Rohnert Park
room_address: 5430 Commerce Blvd Suite 2G Rohnert Park, CA 94928
room_description:
The year is 1984 and you are in Atlantis, an underwater city build by eccentric genius Thomas Neptune. Over the last several years, Neptune has been designing an advanced weapon capable of destroying ships thousands of miles away.

You are an elite team of undercover agents posing as new recruits to Atlantis. Your mission is to deactivate the superweapon so that it can be safely destroyed. Good luck, agents!
